Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.54,CHA,,0,0,0,,好 别急着松手\N{\fs60}Okay, hold on, don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.47,CHA,,0,0,0,,瞄准了吗\N{\fs60}You see where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:15.24,CHA,,0,0,0,,好 现在我们做点儿准备\N{\fs60}Okay. Now, let's worry about how you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,过来一点儿 脚尖朝这边\N{\fs60}Gotta move your foot here. Point your toe this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,转过来点儿\N{\fs60}Your hips here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.52,CHA,,0,0,0,,- 看得见吗 - 可以\N{\fs60}- Can you see? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,确定吗\N{\fs60}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.99,CHA,,0,0,0,,现在呢 还看得见吗\N{\fs60}How about now? Can you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.52,CHA,,0,0,0,,挡住啦 那这样呢\N{\fs60}No. How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.19,CHA,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\fs60}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.93,CHA,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 拉弓\N{\fs60}Ready? Three fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.70,CHA,,0,0,0,,真棒\N{\fs60}Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.50,CHA,,0,0,0,,好球 孩子\N{\fs60}Nice throw, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.87,CHA,,0,0,0,,接着\N{\fs60}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.84,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们是加蛋黄酱还是芥末酱 还是都要\N{\fs60}Hey, you guys want mayo? Or mustard? Or both?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.94,CHA,,0,0,0,,吃热狗谁加蛋黄酱啊\N{\fs60}Who puts mayo on a hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.04,CHA,,0,0,0,,没准你的兄弟要\N{\fs60}Probably your brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.18,CHA,,0,0,0,,来两个加芥末酱的 谢谢啦 亲爱的\N{\fs60}Uh, two mustard, please! Thanks, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:50.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs60}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:52.95,CHA,,0,0,0,,奈特 蛋黄酱还是芥末酱\N{\fs60}Nate, mayo or mustard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:54.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,番茄酱怎么样\N{\fs60}How about ketchup?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.85,CHA,,0,0,0,,番茄酱没问题 我也有\N{\fs60}Or ketchup. I got ketchup, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:58.99,CHA,,0,0,0,,注意肘部\N{\fs60}Mind your elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.94,CHA,,0,0,0,,干得好 小鹰眼 去把箭拿回来\N{\fs60}Good job, hawk-eye. Go get your arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.61,CHA,,0,0,0,,各位 练得差不多啦 饭好啦\N{\fs60}Hey, guys! Enough practice. Soup's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.08,CHA,,0,0,0,,好的 来啦 我们都饿了\N{\fs60}All right. We're coming. We're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:16.74,CHA,,0,0,0,,莱拉 走吧\N{\fs60}Lila, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:20.88,CHA,,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fs60}Lila?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:24.78,CHA,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs60}Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:29.76,CHA,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fs60}Hey, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.80,CHA,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs60}Babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.00,CHA,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs60}Babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.70,CHA,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fs60}Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.97,CHA,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fs60}Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.21,CHA,,0,0,0,,劳拉\N{\fs60}Laura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.12,CHA,,0,0,0,,你不必那样\N{\fs60}You don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.32,CHA,,0,0,0,,你保持这样就好\N{\fs60}Because, uh, you're just holding the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.89,CHA,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs60}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.79,CHA,,0,0,0,,就差一点儿\N{\fs60}That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.73,CHA,,0,0,0,,进了 我们现在一比一平了\N{\fs60}That's a goal. We are now one apiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.40,CHA,,0,0,0,,我想再试一次\N{\fs60}I would like to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.68,CHA,,0,0,0,,现在平局 紧张不紧张 好玩儿吧\N{\fs60}We're tied up. Feel the tension? It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.91,CHA,,0,0,0,,糟糕 现在你有机会赢了\N{\fs60}That was terrible. Now you have a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.23,CHA,,0,0,0,,这样你就赢了 恭喜\N{\fs60}And you've won. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:03.88,CHA,,0,0,0,,公平竞赛\N{\fs60}Fair game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.12,CHA,,0,0,0,,友谊第一\N{\fs60}Good sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.28,CHA,,0,0,0,,好玩儿吗\N{\fs60}You have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.67,CHA,,0,0,0,,好玩儿\N{\fs60}It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:36.68,CHA,,0,0,0,,启动了吗\N{\fs60}This thing on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.95,CHA,,0,0,0,,波兹小姐 佩珀\N{\fs60}Hey, Miss Potts. Pep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.85,CHA,,0,0,0,,你要是发现这段影像\N{\fs60}If you find this recording...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:50.02,CHA,,0,0,0,,可别发到网上去 这个太伤感了\N{\fs60}don't post it on social media. It's gonna be a real tearjerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.70,CHA,,0,0,0,,我不知道你能不能看见这些\N{\fs60}I don't know if you're ever gonna see these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.16,CHA,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道你是不是还…\N{\fs60}I don't even know if you're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.93,CHA,,0,0,0,,老天 希望你没事儿\N{\fs60}Oh, God, I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.27,CHA,,0,0,0,,今天是第二十一天了\N{\fs60}{\i1} Today's day 21.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.21,CHA,,0,0,0,,不对 是第二十二天\N{\fs60}{\i1} No, uh, 22.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:09.17,CHA,,0,0,0,,相比浩瀚的宇宙 我的存在微不足道\N{\fs60}{\i1} You know, if it wasn't{\i0} for the existential terror {\i1} of staring into{\i0} the literal void of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.46,CHA,,0,0,0,,如果不细想 今天我过得还行\N{\fs60}{\i1} I'd say I'm feeling{\i0} a little better today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.17,CHA,,0,0,0,,感染好多了 多亏了有蓝妹妹在这儿\N{\fs60}{\i1} Infection's run its course,{\i0\i1} thanks to{\i0} the Blue Meanie back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,你肯定会喜欢她的\N{\fs60}{\i1} Oh, you'd love her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.89,CHA,,0,0,0,,特别干练\N{\fs60}{\i1} Very practical.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.96,CHA,,0,0,0,,就是下手有点儿重\N{\fs60}{\i1} Only a tiny bit sadistic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.16,CHA,,0,0,0,,燃料舱在作战时炸裂了\N{\fs60}{\i1} So, the fuel cells{\i0} were cracked during battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.43,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们想了个办法利用反向离子充电\N{\fs60}{\i1} and we figured out a way{\i0} to reverse the ion charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.50,CHA,,0,0,0,,争取了大概48小时的飞行时间\N{\fs60}{\i1} and bought ourselves{\i0} about 48 hours of flight time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.44,CHA,,0,0,0,,但是现在没招了\N{\fs60}{\i1} Uh, but it's now dead{\i0} in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.44,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们离最近的便利店还有几千光年呢\N{\fs60}{\i1} Thousand light years{\i0} from the nearest 7-Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.35,CHA,,0,0,0,,氧气只能支撑到明天早上\N{\fs60}{\i1} Oxygen will run out{\i0} tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.32,CHA,,0,0,0,,然后就这样了\N{\fs60}{\i1} and that'll be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:55.52,CHA,,0,0,0,,我曾经说过不会再有意外了\N{\fs60}{\i1} Pep, I know I said{\i0} no more surprises...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,可我真的希望能完成最后的这次任务\N{\fs60}{\i1} but I gotta say{\i0} I was really hoping{\i1} to pull off one last one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.43,CHA,,0,0,0,,但是现在看来…\N{\fs60}{\i1} But it looks like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.80,CHA,,0,0,0,,你也知道的\N{\fs60}{\i1} Well, you know{\i0} what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.80,CHA,,0,0,0,,别太难过\N{\fs60}Don't feel bad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:10.24,CHA,,0,0,0,,我的意思是你可以悲痛几个星期\N{\fs60}I mean, actually, if you grovel for a couple weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.45,CHA,,0,0,0,,然后怀着自责继续生活\N{\fs60}and then move on with enormous guilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:22.99,CHA,,0,0,0,,我得躺下了 闭会儿眼睛\N{\fs60}I should probably lie down for a minute. Go rest my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.29,CHA,,0,0,0,,你要知道\N{\fs60}Please know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:32.13,CHA,,0,0,0,,每天入睡的时候 这些天都一样\N{\fs60}when I drift off, it'll be like every night lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.83,CHA,,0,0,0,,我挺好的一切都挺好\N{\fs60}I'm fine. Totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.53,CHA,,0,0,0,,我会梦到你\N{\fs60}I dream about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.97,CHA,,0,0,0,,梦里一直都是你\N{\fs60}Because it's always you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.17,CHA,,0,0,0,,我没能阻止他\N{\fs60}Couldn't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.31,CHA,,0,0,0,,我也没有\N{\fs60}Neither could I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.08,CHA,,0,0,0,,那孩子牺牲了\N{\fs60}I lost the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.78,CHA,,0,0,0,,托尼 我们都输了\N{\fs60}Tony, we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.79,CHA,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fs60}Is, uh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.48,CHA,,0,0,0,,- 太好了 - 我的天\N{\fs60}- Oh, good. - Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.06,CHA,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs60}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.14,CHA,,0,0,0,,没事儿了\N{\fs60}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.81,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸离开地球己经二十三天了\N{\fs60}It's been 23 days since Thanos came to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.48,CHA,,0,0,0,,各国政府分崩离析\N{\fs60}World governments are in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:47.50,CHA,,0,0,0,,还在运转的部门正在做人口统计\N{\fs60}The parts that are still working are trying to take a census
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.82,CHA,,0,0,0,,根据情况统计\N{\fs60}...and it looks like he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,看来他做的和他说的完全一致\N{\fs60}He did exactly what he said he was gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.29,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸夺走了…\N{\fs60}Thanos wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.63,CHA,,0,0,0,,一半的生命\N{\fs60}...50% of all living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.70,CHA,,0,0,0,,他现在在哪里\N{\fs60}Where is he now? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.60,CHA,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs60}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.67,CHA,,0,0,0,,他打开了一扇传送门然后离开了\N{\fs60}He just opened a portal and walked through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.48,CHA,,0,0,0,,他怎么了\N{\fs60}What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.58,CHA,,0,0,0,,他很生气\N{\fs60}Oh, he's pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.41,CHA,,0,0,0,,他觉得自己失败了\N{\fs60}He thinks he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,确实如此 但谁不是呢\N{\fs60}Which, of course, he did, but there's a lot of that going around, ain't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:26.39,CHA,,0,0,0,,说真的 你不开口说话\N{\fs60}Honestly, until this exact second
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,我以为你是毛绒玩具呢\N{\fs60}I thought you were a Build-A-Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.22,CHA,,0,0,0,,随你的便\N{\fs60}Maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.66,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们三周来一直在搜寻灭霸的踪迹\N{\fs60}We've been hunting Thanos for three weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:34.64,CHA,,0,0,0,,宇宙空间卫星扫描一无所获\N{\fs60}Deep space scans and satellites, and we got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.73,CHA,,0,0,0,,托尼 你和他交过手\N{\fs60}Tony, you fought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.64,CHA,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你的 我没和他交过手\N{\fs60}Who told you that? I didn't fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.45,CHA,,0,0,0,,他把一颗星球砸到我脸上\N{\fs60}No, he wiped my face with a planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:45.10,CHA,,0,0,0,,那个变戏法的就交出原石了\N{\fs60}while the Bleecker Street magician gave away the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.14,CHA,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样 根本没法打 知道了\N{\fs60}That's what happened. There was no fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.28,CHA,,0,0,0,,打不过\N{\fs60} 'cause he's not beatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,他有没有留下线索或坐标之类的\N{\fs60}Did he give you any clues, any coordinates, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.81,CHA,,0,0,0,,我几年前就知道这一切\N{\fs60}I saw this coming a few years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.12,CHA,,0,0,0,,我早就料到了 我不敢相信\N{\fs60}I had a vision. I didn't wanna believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,还以为是一场噩梦\N{\fs60}Thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,托尼 我需要你集中精神\N{\fs60}Tony, I'm gonna need you to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.69,CHA,,0,0,0,,我需要过你\N{\fs60}And I needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.46,CHA,,0,0,0,,那是以前了 比你现在更需要\N{\fs60}As in, past tense. That trumps what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.56,CHA,,0,0,0,,一切都晚了 老兄 抱歉\N{\fs60}It's too late, buddy. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,你知道我现在需要什么吗 我需要刮胡子\N{\fs60}You know what I need? I need a shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.37,CHA,,0,0,0,,而且我记得告诉过你们\N{\fs60}And I believe I remember telling all youse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,托尼 托尼 托尼\N{\fs60}Tony, Tony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.33,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们和那些不在的人\N{\fs60}...alive and otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:20.89,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们需要用战甲把全世界武装起来\N{\fs60}that what we needed was a suit of armor around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:21.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,还记得吗\N{\fs60}Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,不管它是否侵犯了我们宝贵的自由\N{\fs60}Whether it impacted our precious freedoms or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.25,CHA,,0,0,0,,那才是我们真正需要的\N{\fs60}That's what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.45,CHA,,0,0,0,,那条路最后行不通\N{\fs60}Well, that didn't work out, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.92,CHA,,0,0,0,,我说过我们会输的\N{\fs60}I said we'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.68,CHA,,0,0,0,,你说即使输了也一起面对\N{\fs60}You said, "We'll do that together, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.69,CHA,,0,0,0,,结果怎么样 队长 我们输了\N{\fs60}And guess what, Cap? We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.36,CHA,,0,0,0,,而你当时根本不在\N{\fs60}And you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.93,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们就这个水平吗 只能慢人一步吗\N{\fs60}But that's what we do, right? Our best work after the fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.96,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们只能当复仇者吗\N{\fs60}We're the "Avengers."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.66,CHA,,0,0,0,,只能当复仇者 不能当预防者吗\N{\fs60}We're the "Avengers," not the "Pre-vengers."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.60,CHA,,0,0,0,,- 行了 - 是不是啊\N{\fs60}- Okay. - Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.63,CHA,,0,0,0,,你说的够多了 坐下吧 好吧\N{\fs60}You made your point. Just sit down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.73,CHA,,0,0,0,,我还没说完\N{\fs60}Okay. No, no, here's my point. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.84,CHA,,0,0,0,,- 她就挺好 - 托尼 坐下吧\N{\fs60}- She's great by the way. - Tony, you're sick. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.67,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们需要你 你是新生力量\N{\fs60}We need you. You're new blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.67,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们这帮老废物 我没什么可给你的\N{\fs60}Bunch of tired old mules. I got nothing for you, Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:58.18,CHA,,0,0,0,,没有坐标 没有线索 没有战术 没有方案\N{\fs60}I got no coordinates, no clues, no strategies, no options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:02.35,CHA,,0,0,0,,什么都没有 我也不相信你 你这个骗子\N{\fs60}Zero. Zip. Nada. No trust, liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,拿着这个\N{\fs60}Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:10.32,CHA,,0,0,0,,你找到他以后 把这个戴上\N{\fs60}You find him, you put that on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.19,CHA,,0,0,0,,然后躲起来\N{\fs60}you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.90,CHA,,0,0,0,,- 托尼 - 我没事儿\N{\fs60}- Tony! - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.47,CHA,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯给了他一针镇静剂\N{\fs60}Bruce gave him a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.47,CHA,,0,0,0,,他今天可能醒不过来了\N{\fs60}He's gonna probably be out for the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们照顾好他\N{\fs60}You guys take care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.28,CHA,,0,0,0,,我回来时给他带一瓶佐利安灵药\N{\fs60}and I'll bring him a Xorrian elixir when I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:31.41,CHA,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿\N{\fs60}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,去杀灭霸\N{\fs60}To kill Thanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们一般都是团队作战\N{\fs60}You know, we usually work as a team here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.52,CHA,,0,0,0,,再说现在士气也不高\N{\fs60}and, uh, between you and I, morale's a little fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.92,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们知道太空是你的地盘\N{\fs60}We realize up there is more your territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.33,CHA,,0,0,0,,但这也是我们的战斗\N{\fs60}but this is our fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.60,CHA,,0,0,0,,你知道他到底在哪儿吗\N{\fs60}You even know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,我找人问就行\N{\fs60}I know people who might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.30,CHA,,0,0,0,,没必要\N{\fs60}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.54,CHA,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你们灭霸在哪里\N{\fs60}I can tell you where Thanos is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.01,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸用了很长时间使我变得完美\N{\fs60}Thanos spent a long time trying to perfect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:03.38,CHA,,0,0,0,,他一直在给我讲述那个宏大的计划\N{\fs60}And when he worked, he talked about his Great Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.58,CHA,,0,0,0,,即便被大卸八块 我也想讨好他\N{\fs60}Even disassembled, I wanted to please him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.55,CHA,,0,0,0,,我就会问…\N{\fs60}I'd ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.68,CHA,,0,0,0,,大功告成以后 我们将何去何从\N{\fs60}where would we go once his plan was complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,他的回答永远只有一个\N{\fs60}And his answer was always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.83,CHA,,0,0,0,,去那个花园\N{\fs60}"To the Garden."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.50,CHA,,0,0,0,,真够可以的 灭霸居然还有退休计划\N{\fs60}That's cute. Thanos has a retirement plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.37,CHA,,0,0,0,,所以他在哪儿\N{\fs60}So, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.60,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸打完响指后\N{\fs60}When Thanos snapped his fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:30.64,CHA,,0,0,0,,地球成了宇宙级能量涌动的原爆点\N{\fs60}Earth became ground zero for a power surge of ridiculously cosmic proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.94,CHA,,0,0,0,,从没有过这么大的能量\N{\fs60}No one's ever seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.28,CHA,,0,0,0,,直到两天以前\N{\fs60}Until two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:37.51,CHA,,0,0,0,,在这颗星球上\N{\fs60}on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.68,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸就在那里\N{\fs60}Thanos is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,他又用原石了\N{\fs60}He used the stones again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们现在人手短缺吧\N{\fs60}We'd be going in shorthanded, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.06,CHA,,0,0,0,,而且原石还在他手上 所以…\N{\fs60}Look, he's still got the stones, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.82,CHA,,0,0,0,,那就抢回来\N{\fs60}So, let's get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.46,CHA,,0,0,0,,把所有人救回来\N{\fs60}Use them to bring everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.66,CHA,,0,0,0,,就这么简单吗\N{\fs60}Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.46,CHA,,0,0,0,,对 就这么简单\N{\fs60}Yeah. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.73,CHA,,0,0,0,,即便逆转这一切的希望渺茫\N{\fs60}Even if there's a small chance that we can undo this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.64,CHA,,0,0,0,,为了逝去的战友 我们也必须竭尽全力去试试\N{\fs60}I mean, we owe it to everyone who's not in this room to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.40,CHA,,0,0,0,,如果我们这么做了\N{\fs60}If we do this, how do we know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.74,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们怎么知道结局会和之前不一样\N{\fs60}it's gonna end any differently than it did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,因为之前你们没有我\N{\fs60}Because before you didn't have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.48,CHA,,0,0,0,,嘿 新来的\N{\fs60}Hey, new girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.01,CHA,,0,0,0,,这个屋子里的人多少也都算超级英雄\N{\fs60}Everybody in this room is about that superhero life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,我倒要问问这么长时间你去哪儿了\N{\fs60}And if you don't mind my asking, where the hell have you been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.82,CHA,,0,0,0,,宇宙里的星球很多\N{\fs60}There are a lot of other planets in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,可惜没有你们这样的人守护\N{\fs60}And unfortunately, they didn't have you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.95,CHA,,0,0,0,,我觉得她不错\N{\fs60}I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:50.14,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们去干掉这个混蛋\N{\fs60}Let's go get this son of a bitch.
