Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.46,CHA,,0,0,0,,好吧 谁没来过太空\N{\fs60}Okay. Who here hasn't been to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.71,CHA,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs60}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.58,CHA,,0,0,0,,可别在我的船上吐出来\N{\fs60}You better not throw up on my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.67,CHA,,0,0,0,,启动跳跃 三 二一\N{\fs60}Approaching jump in three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.85,CHA,,0,0,0,,我先去侦察一下\N{\fs60}{\i1}I'll head down for recon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.52,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们会成功的 史蒂夫\N{\fs60}This is gonna work, Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs60}I know it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.76,CHA,,0,0,0,,除了成功我别无选择\N{\fs60}'Cause I don't know what I'm gonna do if it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:10.50,CHA,,0,0,0,,没有卫星 没有舰船\N{\fs60}{\i1} No satellites.{\i0} No ships. No armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.97,CHA,,0,0,0,,没有军队 没有任何地面防御\N{\fs60}{\i1} No ground defenses{\i0} of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.20,CHA,,0,0,0,,只有他一个人\N{\fs60}{\i1} It's just him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.91,CHA,,0,0,0,,那就够了\N{\fs60}And that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.24,CHA,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs60}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.81,CHA,,0,0,0,,原石在哪里\N{\fs60}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.98,CHA,,0,0,0,,回答他的问题\N{\fs60}Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.65,CHA,,0,0,0,,宇宙需要被校正\N{\fs60}The universe required correction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:12.26,CHA,,0,0,0,,在那之后 原石除了诱惑再无他用\N{\fs60}After that, the stones served no purpose beyond temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.20,CHA,,0,0,0,,你杀害了无数生命\N{\fs60}You murdered trillions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.03,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们应该为之感恩\N{\fs60}You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.10,CHA,,0,0,0,,原石在哪里\N{\fs60}Where are the stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:26.32,CHA,,0,0,0,,不在了 一切归为尘埃\N{\fs60}Gone. Reduced to atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.07,CHA,,0,0,0,,你两天前才刚刚用过\N{\fs60}You used them two days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.04,CHA,,0,0,0,,我使用原石摧毁了原石\N{\fs60}I used the stones to destroy the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.08,CHA,,0,0,0,,这几乎要了我的命\N{\fs60}It nearly killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.21,CHA,,0,0,0,,但我的使命完成了\N{\fs60}But the work is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,注定如此\N{\fs60}It always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:45.15,CHA,,0,0,0,,我就是…天命\N{\fs60}I am inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.79,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们好好找找 他肯定在说谎\N{\fs60}We have to tear this place apart. He has to be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.86,CHA,,0,0,0,,我父亲什么都干得出来\N{\fs60}My father is many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.96,CHA,,0,0,0,,但他从不说谎\N{\fs60}A liar is not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.10,CHA,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 女儿\N{\fs60}Thank you, daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.30,CHA,,0,0,0,,也许我对你太苛刻了\N{\fs60}Perhaps I treated you too harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.18,CHA,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs60}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.62,CHA,,0,0,0,,你干了什么\N{\fs60}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.19,CHA,,0,0,0,,这次我是冲着头去的\N{\fs60}I went for the head.
