Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:09.69,NBD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fn华文中宋\b1\pos(960,480)\c&HC8C8C8&}年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:09.69,NBD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fn华文中宋\b1\pos(1160,480)\c&HC8C8C8&}后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.79,CHA,,0,0,0,,所以 我…\N{\fs60}{\i1} So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:34.18,NBD,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs66\b1\c&H53662B&\pos(894,750)}他们不在了,\N我们何去何从?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.29,CHA,,0,0,0,,我约人出去吃了个饭\N{\fs60}...I, uh, went on a date the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.16,CHA,,0,0,0,,五年以来第一次\N{\fs60}It's the first time in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:42.08,CHA,,0,0,0,,我坐在餐桌那里 不知道该说些什么\N{\fs60}You know? I'm sitting there at dinner. I didn't even know what to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,你们聊了什么\N{\fs60}What did you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.79,CHA,,0,0,0,,还是那些废话 一切都变了\N{\fs60}Eh, same old crap. You know, how things have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.31,CHA,,0,0,0,,我的工作 他的工作\N{\fs60}My job, his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.75,CHA,,0,0,0,,我们有多么想念大都会球队\N{\fs60}How much we miss the Mets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.35,CHA,,0,0,0,,后来我们都沉默了\N{\fs60}And then things got quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:03.09,CHA,,0,0,0,,然后他在上沙拉的时候哭了\N{\fs60}then he cried as they were serving the salads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.76,CHA,,0,0,0,,那你呢\N{\fs60}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.77,CHA,,0,0,0,,我也哭了 在上甜点的时候\N{\fs60}I cried just before dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.40,CHA,,0,0,0,,但是我们明天还会见面 所以…\N{\fs60}But I'm seeing him again tomorrow, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.94,CHA,,0,0,0,,很好 你克服了最艰难的时刻\N{\fs60}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.74,CHA,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道结果会怎么样\N{\fs60}You did the hardest part. You took the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,你还是迈出了新的一步\N{\fs60}You didn't know where you were gonna come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:25.91,CHA,,0,0,0,,就是这样 我们总要迈出这样的一小步\N{\fs60}And that's it. That's those little brave baby steps we gotta take...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:30.35,CHA,,0,0,0,,让我们重新振作起来 重新找到方向\N{\fs60}to try and become whole again, try and find purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.05,CHA,,0,0,0,,1945年我被封在冰里\N{\fs60}I went in the ice in '45,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.26,CHA,,0,0,0,,那之前我刚遇到一生至爱\N{\fs60}right after I met the love of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.16,CHA,,0,0,0,,直到七十年后我才醒来\N{\fs60}Woke up 70 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.97,CHA,,0,0,0,,但是你必须要继续前行\N{\fs60}You gotta move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.34,CHA,,0,0,0,,继续生活\N{\fs60}Gotta move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:55.01,CHA,,0,0,0,,世界的命运在你我手中\N{\fs60}The world is in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:59.15,CHA,,0,0,0,,这是我们的使命 我们责无旁贷\N{\fs60}It's left to us, guys. And we gotta do something with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.92,CHA,,0,0,0,,否则…\N{\fs60}Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.41,CHA,,0,0,0,,灭霸本可以杀掉我们所有人\N{\fs60}Thanos should've killed all of us.